# Docker build cache configuration
# This file is used to configure NuGet package caching across builds

# Instructions for using this cache:
# 1. Build with BuildKit enabled: DOCKER_BUILDKIT=1 docker build ...
# 2. Use BuildKit cache mount for maximum efficiency
# 3. For docker-compose: COMPOSE_DOCKER_CLI_BUILD=1 DOCKER_BUILDKIT=1 docker-compose build

# The Dockerfiles have been optimized with:
# - Layer caching for restore steps
# - NUGET_PACKAGES environment variable
# - Copy project files before code files
# - --verbosity quiet and --no-restore flags

# To clear the cache:
# docker builder prune -af

